MBC College Music Festival.

352
00:41:34,730 --> 00:41:36,060
This will be the last team!

353
00:41:36,060 --> 00:41:37,600
Contestant number 18!

354
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:40,970
Representing Seoul, this is the band "Sharp." Yonsei University...

355
00:41:40,970 --> 00:41:43,560
It's really competitive this year, too.

356
00:41:43,560 --> 00:41:45,150
I wonder who will win the grand prize?

357
00:41:45,150 --> 00:41:49,170
I think the medical students might win!

358
00:41:49,170 --> 00:41:51,590
- You think so?
- They were really good.

359
00:41:51,590 --> 00:41:52,420
Did you like that song?

360
00:41:52,420 --> 00:41:53,230
Contestant number 18.

361
00:41:53,230 --> 00:41:56,580
